channel.title: [BCEL] Updater
channel.description:
This is a runescape updater i made for [url=http://rs-hacking.com/index.php/topic,6.0.html]www.rs-hacking.com[/url],
Credits: saevion frank_ psb
the main reason for creating this is to put a stop to [b]bad style[/b] updaters. [b]but by no means is it perfect.[/b] enjoy :)

ri has interface Item getStacksize() returns int ri.p getID() returns int ri.s
pc has interface CachedItem getItem() returns Item pc.y
we has interface Npc getComposite() returns tf we.oc
bl has interface Player getPrayerHeadIcon() returns int bl.Mc getPkHeadIcon() returns int bl.Hc getTeam() returns int bl.mc getCombatLevel() returns int bl.Ac getName() returns String bl.Gc

oi has interface Scene getAnimating() returns boolean oi.m
